import React from "react";

export default function tradingSvg(props) {
  const { fill } = props;
  return (
    <svg
      width="24px"
      height="24px"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    >
      <path
        d="M3 17L3 7L10 7"
        stroke={fill}
        strokeWidth="1.5"
        strokeLinecap="round"
        strokeLinejoin="round"
      />
      <path
        d="M3 12H8"
        stroke={fill}
        strokeWidth="1.5"
        strokeLinecap="round"
        strokeLinejoin="round"
      />
      <path
        d="M13 17L17 12M17 12L21 7M17 12L13 7M17 12L21 17"
        stroke={fill}
        strokeWidth="1.5"
        strokeLinecap="round"
        strokeLinejoin="round"
      />
    </svg>
  );
}
